Is there a funny sound coming from somewhere in your car? Are you unsure about which car to buy because of your budget? Do you want to know something about your motorbike? Or, do you need to learn how to change a tyre? #Trending is starting a new column where, once a month, a motoring expert will answer all your burning questions. Send us your questions and be as specific as possible – the more information you give us, the easier it’ll be for us to answer your questions. Using the words CAR QUESTIONS in the subject line, email justus.visagie@media24.com. You can also SMS the keywords CAR QUESTIONS and your question to 35697. Please include your name. SMSes cost R1.50.